ascend_skill.desc: Increase the skill levels of Healing Grace and Thief Tactics by 3.

ascend_skill.desc: Highlight Enhanced: The duration of the max HP increase and healing effect increase are extended by 1 turn.

highlight_skill.desc:
Restore party's HP by 17.6%/17.6%/18.6%/18.6% of Minami's max HP + 1500/1824/1844/2168, and cure 1 debuff.
Increase party's max HP by 16.5% of Minami's max HP (up to 2326/2326/2697/2697) for 2 turns. At the end of an action, restore HP equal to 6.5%/6.5%/6.9%/6.9% of Minami's max HP + 556/676/683/803 for 1 turn.

normal_skill.desc:

Also restore HP of the ally with the lowest HP with this effect 2 times.
For each Diagnosis stack, activate this effect 1 more time.
For each Diagnosis stack spent, increase the max HP of allies (other than Minami) by 7.5% of Minami's max HP for 2 turns (up to 1057/1057/1226/1226).
normal_skill.name: Compassionate Cure
